    6. Third-Party Services &amp; Sponsors
  </h3>
  <p>We use the following third-party services:</p>
  <ul style="padding-left:20px;">
    <li><strong>Google Analytics (GA4)</strong> &mdash; collects anonymised usage data to help us
    understand traffic patterns. Data is processed by Google under their
    <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-weight:500;">Privacy Policy</a>.
