  <!-- 7 -->
  <h3 style="margin-top:28px;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e7eb;padding-bottom:6px;">
    <i class="fas fa-user-check" style="color:var(--primary);margin-right:6px;font-size:14px;" aria-hidden="true"></i>
    7. Your Rights
  </h3>
  <p>Under the <strong>GDPR</strong> and other international data-protection laws, you can:</p>
  <ul style="padding-left:20px;">
    <li><strong>Access</strong> your data &mdash; ask us for a copy of what we hold.</li>
    <li><strong>Correct</strong> inaccurate information.</li>
    <li><strong>Delete</strong> your data (&ldquo;right to be forgotten&rdquo;). Because everything is
    in-memory, it&rsquo;s automatically erased on server restart. Logging out also removes your session
    immediately.</li>
    <li><strong>Withdraw consent</strong> at any time &mdash; simply stop using the app.</li>
    <li><strong>Port</strong> your data &mdash; request it in a structured, machine-readable format.</li>
    <li><strong>Object</strong> to specific processing activities.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>To exercise any of these rights, reach out through
    <a href="https://training.rcvacademy.com/support" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-weight:500;">training.rcvacademy.com/support</a>.</p>

  <!-- 7 -->
